[[File:Bouncers.jpg|thumb|right|250px|A pair of tough brutes, the [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] bouncers were.]]

The '''[[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] bouncers''' worked in [[Baruk's Bar]]. When [[Kyle Katarn]] entered the bar, [[Unidentified Rodian (Bryar pistol)|one of the Rodians]] told him to hand over his weapons, promising to give them back when he would leave. However, they, along with everyone else in the bar, attacked Katarn as part of a trap their conspecific boss, [[Reelo Baruk]], had laid for him. Along with everyone else in the bar&mdash;apart from the [[Baldarek|bartender]]&mdash;they wound up [[Death/Legends|dead]].

==Behind the scenes==
The Rodian bouncers are [[canon]]ical, appearing in [[Star Wars: Jedi Knight II: Jedi Outcast|''Jedi Knight II: Jedi Outcast'']], in which they have some dialogue with the player. However, they have yet to be named.

